{"tid":1442231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急需要大量文宣講點解要繼續抗爭落去","createTime":"2019-08-11T01:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:12:35.000Z","uid":41389,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1becd4b3687798c501d7632d47411e3f229d8e31","tid":1442231,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:28:22.000Z","msg":"好多人開始攰 抗爭疲勞 想回復正常生活<br />\n<br />\n而又有好多中間派日日比cctvb洗腦<br />\n見啲義士出黎但無明確目標<br />\n又係心理疲勞<br />\n都開始靠番政府個邊<br />\n<br />\n2個月啦<br />\n黎明前既黑暗係最撚黑暗<br />\n希望大家勇武之餘<br />\n唔好唔記得低成本支線任<br />\n幫手明確番我地既目標 市民同國際社會既認受性<br />\n唔好比林奠同4點鐘驚犬成日老屈<br />\neg文宣 連儂牆 cctvb轉台 轉美金 老豆搵仔 機場文宣等等<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4ae57b64cc17ff2fbc147d9caa72284e7e28b2d8","tid":1442231,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:29:11.000Z","msg":"仲有連儂電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地需要多啲高汁合成片"},{"pid":"6d918aff076cbd3fb245f82b146b30a8403f0660","tid":1442231,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:29:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"834925f4237362b21559318c8b076983032e4ea8","tid":1442231,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"474fce79df01df49931e9edd194ed294ec3ed34a","tid":1442231,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:29:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56774ba0e31c8326d438573e6be356a06177e448","tid":1442231,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:30:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc00a2bcf05c438b2943452a14dff55acb644b03","tid":1442231,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T01:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class